622
00:35:17,560 --> 00:35:19,679
I blew it.

623
00:35:20,840 --> 00:35:21,879
Let's go.

624
00:35:29,080 --> 00:35:31,159
Let's go now.

625
00:35:32,600 --> 00:35:33,919
