The grade report is out.

626
00:35:34,679 --> 00:35:35,280
Excuse me.

627
00:35:35,280 --> 00:35:36,639
How's my result that bad?

628
00:35:36,800 --> 00:35:37,919
Look.

629
00:35:39,239 --> 00:35:40,320
