I did improve.

630
00:35:41,080 --> 00:35:41,800
I've improved by one rank.

631
00:35:41,919 --> 00:35:42,919
As expected,

632
00:35:43,080 --> 00:35:44,679
I could get out of the last ten

633
00:35:44,879 --> 00:35:46,760
