637
00:35:52,479 --> 00:35:53,600
In a minute.

638
00:35:54,280 --> 00:35:55,159
Alright now. Let's go.

639
00:35:55,280 --> 00:35:57,080
Let's get back to our studies.

640
00:36:18,320 --> 00:36:20,560
